body_html:
@mrry
I'm also getting worse accuracy (usually) for wide_n_deep compare to just wide. The values do fluctuate since I'm using 980 GTX GPU. But the values seems to fluctuate only for the wide_n_deep accuracies (I've gotten as high as .840 and as low as .796), the wide is fixed (always get 0.835452 with GPU).
This is using the wide_n_deep_tutorial.py as of 9/9/2016
running with
Anaconda 3.5
Tensorflow 0.10.0rc0
Ubuntu 16.04
